Sequel
The Great Khan () is the provisional title73 for the second installment of semi-historical film series by Sergei Bodrov based on the life of Tem&lt;U+00FC&gt;jin, Genghis Khan. The Mongolian pop singer, Amarkhuu Borkhuu, was offered a role in the movie but he declined.74
